1
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come in.</font>

2
00:00:31,470 --> 00:00:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I kept you waiting.</font>

3
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father's stories of the past 
just never run dry.</font>

4
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be tired.</font>

5
00:00:40,010 --> 00:00:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are so many guests here 
for the wedding as well.</font>

6
00:00:42,610 --> 00:00:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

7
00:00:44,030 --> 00:00:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's lovely to have so many 
people congratulating me.</font>

8
00:00:47,510 --> 00:00:50,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am truly blessed.</font>

9
00:00:52,250 --> 00:00:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a present for you.</font>

10
00:00:54,370 --> 00:00:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

11
00:00:55,290 --> 00:00:57,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope you like it.</font>

12
00:01:01,890 --> 00:01:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's in your color.</font>

13
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:07,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy to receive this. 
It's adorable.</font>

14
00:01:07,170 --> 00:01:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad.</font>

15
00:01:08,710 --> 00:01:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I actually designed this myself.</font>

16
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

17
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It took some time to complete.</font>

18
00:01:14,470 --> 00:01:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I was able to 
give it to you today.</font>

19
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Aqua did all that for me?</i></font>

20
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I put it on?</font>

21
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

22
00:01:25,900 --> 00:01:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it suits you.</font>

23
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Prince Aqua.</font>

24
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, um...</font>

25
00:01:34,940 --> 00:01:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua.</font>

26
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done.</font>

27
00:01:42,940 --> 00:01:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You feel so nice.</font>

28
00:01:45,220 --> 00:01:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could touch you like this forever.</font>

29
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:50,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never get tired of it either.</font>

30
00:01:51,970 --> 00:01:53,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then...</font>

31
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">like husband, like wife, eh?</font>

32
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom, what's that?</font>

33
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

34
00:02:27,670 --> 00:02:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an2}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="28"><b><font color="#f76bb3">The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
<font color="#6b3e34">by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

35
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><b><font color="#6b3e34"><font size="25">A <font color="#f76bb3"><b>Love</b> <font color="#6b3e34">Like <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Ripples</b> <font color="#6b3e34">on the Water</font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font></font>

36
00:03:50,740 --> 00:03:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my!</font>

37
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That dress looks lovely on you, too!</font>

38
00:03:54,660 --> 00:03:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it truly does!</font>

39
00:03:56,780 --> 00:04:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be entrusted with making dresses 
for Lady Tiararose, our future queen...</font>

40
00:04:01,350 --> 00:04:03,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How lucky I am to be a designer!</font>

41
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:06,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you... but...</font>

42
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you've made a few too many.</font>

43
00:04:08,810 --> 00:04:10,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?!</font>

44
00:04:10,660 --> 00:04:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll have many new duties as a consort! 
This isn't even enough!</font>

45
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Really?</font>

46
00:04:16,930 --> 00:04:20,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, they say there's something 
strange about the sea recently.</font>

47
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sea?</font>

48
00:04:22,570 --> 00:04:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I haven't seen it myself,</font>

49
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I hear its color is 
a bit different from usual.</font>

50
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if something's 
happened to the sea fairies.</font>

51
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right. It could be 
the sea fairies playing a joke.</font>

52
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

53
00:04:40,590 --> 00:04:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a great success!</font>

54
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something smells nice, Tiara.</font>

55
00:04:47,550 --> 00:04:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back, Prince Aqua.</font>

56
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:52,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Tiara.</font>

57
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:55,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I love my husband so, so much.</i></font>

58
00:04:55,980 --> 00:04:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm the only one in the world 
who gets to see this expression.</i></font>

59
00:04:58,830 --> 00:05:02,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We've lived together for a year, 
and our wedding is over,</i></font>

60
00:05:02,990 --> 00:05:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but he still makes my heart race.</i></font>

61
00:05:07,290 --> 00:05:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see you made the cookies I asked for.</font>

62
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I tried making them in animal shapes.</font>

63
00:05:14,710 --> 00:05:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?</i></font>

64
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something wrong?</font>

65
00:05:17,450 --> 00:05:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, no. Would you like to taste one?</font>

66
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

67
00:05:30,970 --> 00:05:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just this once, okay?</font>

68
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Prince Aqua!</font>

69
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:42,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you're sweeter 
than any cookie, Tiara.</font>

70
00:05:42,910 --> 00:05:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, please... You're embarrassing me.</font>

71
00:05:45,540 --> 00:05:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're married now. What's the problem?</font>

72
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:52,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'll make some tea.</font>

73
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:01,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something's definitely off.</font>

74
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some of the cookies 
I baked are missing.</font>

75
00:06:05,010 --> 00:06:07,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure there were ten of them.</font>

76
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Last night, too...</i></font>

77
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wasn't mistaken when 
I thought some had disappeared.</i></font>

78
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But how?</i></font>

79
00:06:16,010 --> 00:06:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Tiararose, is something the matter?</font>

80
00:06:20,490 --> 00:06:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, dear. Your cookies?</font>

81
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And none of us would have taken them 
without permission, so...</font>

82
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it have been the forest fairies?</font>

83
00:06:32,610 --> 00:06:37,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can't imagine the fairies 
just taking them without asking.</font>

84
00:06:37,130 --> 00:06:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True...</font>

85
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? The sweets you made 
are disappearing?</font>

86
00:06:51,150 --> 00:06:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't know anything.</font>

87
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:55,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we took any without asking, 
the king would be mad!</font>

88
00:06:55,730 --> 00:06:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought so.</font>

89
00:06:57,380 --> 00:07:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know if there are any spells 
that could make cookies disappear?</font>

90
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:05,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm... We don't know 
any mean magic like that.</font>

91
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:08,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We only like fun things!</font>

92
00:07:08,490 --> 00:07:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's true, isn't it?</font>

93
00:07:10,170 --> 00:07:14,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you all. 
Would you like to have these?</font>

94
00:07:14,910 --> 00:07:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

95
00:07:17,130 --> 00:07:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! We'd love to have them!</font>

96
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... I wonder what I should do...</font>

97
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed...</font>

98
00:07:29,060 --> 00:07:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not try asking Prince Aquasteed?</font>

99
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua is very busy 
with his official duties.</font>

100
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't trouble him with something 
as silly as disappearing cookies.</font>

101
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back.</font>

102
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back.</font>

103
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I'm a bit late.</font>

104
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:50,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

105
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been working very hard.</font>

106
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did anything happen today?</font>

107
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I was fitted for a dress 
and made some sweets.</font>

108
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

109
00:08:09,180 --> 00:08:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strange things are happening 
in Tiara's vicinity?</font>

110
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. It's unclear whether 
anyone wishes her harm,</font>

111
00:08:16,010 --> 00:08:19,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but Philine informed me 
that we should remain alert.</font>

112
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And... it seems Lady Tiararose 
was reluctant to speak to you about it.</font>

113
00:08:26,530 --> 00:08:29,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That's just like her.</font>

114
00:08:31,610 --> 00:08:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Honestly, she's just too precious.</i></font>

115
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How can I get her to tell me?</i></font>

116
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Prince Aqua?</font>

117
00:08:42,540 --> 00:08:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

118
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Tiara?</font>

119
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:49,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Th-That face! He totally knows!</i></font>

120
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's going to pamper me until 
I tell him what happened today!</i></font>

121
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:59,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-The truth is, earlier today...</font>

122
00:08:59,770 --> 00:09:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, you're caving already?</font>

123
00:09:04,060 --> 00:09:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't act so disappointed.</font>

124
00:09:07,510 --> 00:09:10,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was all set to use this 
opportunity to pamper you.</font>

125
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Disappearing cookies, huh?</font>

126
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:18,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It makes more sense to believe this is 
the work of fairies rather than humans.</font>

127
00:09:18,340 --> 00:09:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but...</font>

128
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the forest fairies would never do this.</font>

129
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll look into it.</font>

130
00:09:29,130 --> 00:09:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to worry about a thing.</font>

131
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:35,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But aren't you already busy with work?</font>

132
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:39,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A few of my cookies 
disappearing isn't a big deal.</font>

133
00:09:39,530 --> 00:09:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it is. 
Your cookies belong to me, after all.</font>

134
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, honestly! Even my cookies?</font>

135
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're awfully greedy.</font>

136
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

137
00:09:51,350 --> 00:09:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moment I made you mine, I decided 
I wasn't going to hold back anymore.</font>

138
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So don't worry. 
Just leave everything to me.</font>

139
00:10:00,710 --> 00:10:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

140
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

141
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King!</font>

142
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're back!</font>

143
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:51,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You brought those sweets here again?</font>

144
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:54,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Icilla just seems so sad.</font>

145
00:10:54,230 --> 00:10:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She always seemed so happy before,</font>

146
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:58,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but now she almost never smiles.</font>

147
00:10:58,780 --> 00:10:59,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want one?</font>

148
00:11:00,180 --> 00:11:02,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Throw that thing away!</font>

149
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:05,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dislike sweets made by humans.</font>

150
00:11:06,540 --> 00:11:08,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love is worthless.</font>

151
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="24"><b>The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

152
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something on your mind?</font>

153
00:11:30,420 --> 00:11:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... No.</font>

154
00:11:32,820 --> 00:11:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just seems so strange since 
I know the sea fairies don't like me.</font>

155
00:11:37,870 --> 00:11:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy they want to eat my sweets,</font>

156
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's a complicated feeling.</font>

157
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's hard to believe 
they'd do this to harass her.</i></font>

158
00:11:49,060 --> 00:11:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope Lady Icilla will know something.</font>

159
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no one in this country 
the sea fairies love more than her.</font>

160
00:11:57,800 --> 00:12:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure she'll help us.</font>

161
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

162
00:12:04,190 --> 00:12:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness has told me everything.</font>

163
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm very sorry to make you worry.</font>

164
00:12:10,830 --> 00:12:14,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were the only one we could 
think of who might be able to help.</font>

165
00:12:18,820 --> 00:12:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure where I should start.</font>

166
00:12:23,190 --> 00:12:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there's anything you 
know, please tell us.</font>

167
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never knew rejection 
could hurt this much.</i></font>

168
00:12:37,530 --> 00:12:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I promised I'd give them my blessing,</i></font>

169
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:42,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I just can't stop crying...</i></font>

170
00:12:44,140 --> 00:12:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla is sad.</font>

171
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes us sad, too.</font>

172
00:12:47,830 --> 00:12:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go bully that Tiararose lady 
who took her true love from her!</font>

173
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

174
00:12:58,800 --> 00:13:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could never tell them that.</i></font>

175
00:13:01,490 --> 00:13:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want to hurt them or make them 
worry about things they shouldn't.</i></font>

176
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla?</font>

177
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think...</font>

178
00:13:09,950 --> 00:13:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go see the Sea Fairy King.</font>

179
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've never met before,</font>

180
00:13:16,850 --> 00:13:19,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I know how to get there.</font>

181
00:13:19,410 --> 00:13:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to ask the Sea Fairy King 
to make things right?</font>

182
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:27,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Could you give me just 
a little bit of time?</font>

183
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:31,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. We'll be counting on you.</font>

184
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

185
00:13:33,770 --> 00:13:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This has turned into 
a bigger matter than I thought.</i></font>

186
00:13:37,340 --> 00:13:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to trouble you 
with something like this.</font>

187
00:13:47,350 --> 00:13:49,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Tiararose...</font>

188
00:13:50,090 --> 00:13:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the reason the sea fairies 
stole your cookies.</font>

189
00:13:55,980 --> 00:14:00,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? It was because of you?</font>

190
00:14:00,490 --> 00:14:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes... because I...</font>

191
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla.</font>

192
00:14:15,140 --> 00:14:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla.</font>

193
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry... I...</font>

194
00:14:19,420 --> 00:14:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need 
to force yourself to tell us,</font>

195
00:14:22,710 --> 00:14:25,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so please don't worry about it.</font>

196
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It hasn't caused any trouble for me.</font>

197
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can just make more cookies.</font>

198
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for understanding my 
difficulty in telling you the reason.</font>

199
00:14:40,470 --> 00:14:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise I will see the Sea Fairy King.</font>

200
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These desserts are delicious!</font>

201
00:14:49,530 --> 00:14:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad you like them.</font>

202
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:53,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you know?</font>

203
00:14:53,450 --> 00:14:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Tiararose's tea parties</font>

204
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are known among noble ladies 
as "forest tea parties."</font>

205
00:15:00,050 --> 00:15:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because everyone living in Marinforest 
admires you, Lady Tiararose.</font>

206
00:15:05,350 --> 00:15:07,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That includes us, of course!</font>

207
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

208
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much.</font>

209
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm also happy to have this opportunity 
to talk to all of you.</font>

210
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm in the world of an otome game,</i></font>

211
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:26,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but it has a history going back 
to the very distant past.</i></font>

212
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so interesting.</i></font>

213
00:15:28,430 --> 00:15:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It makes me realize that even though 
it was a game, it's still reality,</i></font>

214
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and that I really am living my own life.</i></font>

215
00:15:50,610 --> 00:15:52,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodness...</font>

216
00:15:53,070 --> 00:15:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I never knew there was 
such an age in history.</font>

217
00:15:56,310 --> 00:15:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this? Did you see 
something interesting in there?</font>

218
00:15:59,990 --> 00:16:02,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, there were 
dessert-baking competitions...</font>

219
00:16:03,340 --> 00:16:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

220
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who is that?</i></font>

221
00:16:09,610 --> 00:16:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't sense anyone there at all.</i></font>

222
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tarmo is still standing guard.</i></font>

223
00:16:16,970 --> 00:16:20,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it possible to get so close 
without anyone noticing?</i></font>

224
00:16:22,500 --> 00:16:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What a pretty lady...</i></font>

225
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:27,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-What's the right way to speak to her?</i></font>

226
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... and you are?</font>

227
00:16:29,610 --> 00:16:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes. I haven't introduced myself.</font>

228
00:16:32,710 --> 00:16:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Claire, the Sky Fairy King.</font>

229
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry! Where are my manners?</font>

230
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Tiararose Lapis Marinforest.</font>

231
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come now, there's 
no need to be so formal.</font>

232
00:16:49,090 --> 00:16:50,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can relax.</font>

233
00:16:58,930 --> 00:17:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to have some?</font>

234
00:17:01,310 --> 00:17:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you! I'd love to!</font>

235
00:17:03,710 --> 00:17:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've prepared tea.</font>

236
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

237
00:17:09,110 --> 00:17:11,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I baked these. They're cheese tarts.</font>

238
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They look delicious. I love cheese.</font>

239
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, they are delicious!</font>

240
00:17:21,270 --> 00:17:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad!</font>

241
00:17:23,340 --> 00:17:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew Prince Aqua had received 
the blessing of the sky, but...</i></font>

242
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:31,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to see Aquasteed's princess.</font>

243
00:17:31,910 --> 00:17:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

244
00:17:33,270 --> 00:17:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What will I do if the Sky Fairy King 
brands me as unworthy of him?</i></font>

245
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right. I'm not going to eat you.</font>

246
00:17:43,890 --> 00:17:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm sorry... I was just...</font>

247
00:17:46,810 --> 00:17:50,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right. I'm the one 
who dropped in unannounced.</font>

248
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:54,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm glad to see that Aquasteed's 
princess is such a nice girl.</font>

249
00:17:57,750 --> 00:18:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your magic is in these, isn't it?</font>

250
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's strange, but it feels comfortable.</font>

251
00:18:02,570 --> 00:18:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm embarrassed to admit it, 
but magic is not my strongest suit.</font>

252
00:18:07,270 --> 00:18:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only thing I'm good at is 
putting a bit of it into my desserts.</font>

253
00:18:12,740 --> 00:18:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fairies don't particularly 
need to eat, you know.</font>

254
00:18:17,450 --> 00:18:21,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I envy you for being able to 
make such delicious treats.</font>

255
00:18:24,230 --> 00:18:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd be happy to help you 
at any time, if you'll have me.</font>

256
00:18:28,490 --> 00:18:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll make some delicious 
sweets for you, King Claire.</font>

257
00:18:33,230 --> 00:18:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so kind.</font>

258
00:18:35,140 --> 00:18:38,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps I'll take you up on that offer.</font>

259
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:41,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was hoping to find some female friends.</font>

260
00:18:41,430 --> 00:18:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too!</font>

261
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After that, King Claire started 
attending my tea parties often, but...</i></font>

262
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:53,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, Aquasteed...</font>

263
00:18:53,330 --> 00:18:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was finally enjoying some 
girls-only time with Tiararose.</font>

264
00:18:55,950 --> 00:18:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's ruined when there's a boy here.</font>

265
00:18:58,510 --> 00:19:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're one to talk.</font>

266
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy for the opportunity 
to have tea with both of you.</font>

267
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, Tiararose!</font>

268
00:19:06,170 --> 00:19:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so sweet and honest!</font>

269
00:19:09,630 --> 00:19:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua, this is embarrassing.</font>

270
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look happy, though.</font>

271
00:19:16,470 --> 00:19:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh, you two are so lovey-dovey.</font>

272
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not fair that Aquasteed 
gets all the attention.</font>

273
00:19:21,820 --> 00:19:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get any closer to Tiara 
than necessary.</font>

274
00:19:24,800 --> 00:19:27,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll have less of my cute Tiara.</font>

275
00:19:27,230 --> 00:19:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you won't.</font>

276
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:33,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you keep tying her down like that, 
she'll get sick of you.</font>

277
00:19:33,860 --> 00:19:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not possible.</font>

278
00:19:35,570 --> 00:19:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara is precious to me.</font>

279
00:19:38,300 --> 00:19:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll never let her go.</font>

280
00:19:40,610 --> 00:19:42,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua...</font>

281
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:48,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, please don't say such embarrassing 
things in front of King Claire!</font>

282
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The waves are more intense than usual.</i></font>

283
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something really is off with the sea.</i></font>

284
00:20:07,360 --> 00:20:10,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought it seemed to look 
murkier than usual at times,</i></font>

285
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I thought I was imagining it.</i></font>

286
00:20:13,310 --> 00:20:17,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How could this have happened 
while I was watching over the seas?</i></font>

287
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no one here.</i></font>

288
00:20:49,850 --> 00:20:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

289
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Fairy King's chamber?</font>

290
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome, Icilla.</font>

291
00:21:07,830 --> 00:21:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's an honor to meet you.</font>

292
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Icilla Pearllant.</font>

293
00:21:13,230 --> 00:21:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, very good.</font>

294
00:21:16,220 --> 00:21:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, what is your business here?</font>

295
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, Your Majesty. 
With all due respect...</font>

296
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's about Crown Princess 
Tiararose Lapis Marinforest,</font>

297
00:21:25,150 --> 00:21:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the wife of the crown prince 
of my homeland.</font>

298
00:21:30,530 --> 00:21:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that?</font>

299
00:21:37,430 --> 00:21:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Why would you do such a thing?</font>

300
00:21:40,280 --> 00:21:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

301
00:21:42,770 --> 00:21:44,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That should be obvious.</font>

302
00:21:45,420 --> 00:21:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I absolutely hate Tiararose.</font>

303
00:21:49,910 --> 00:21:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

304
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="25"><font color="#3d8afc"><b><font color="#f76bb3">Whisper</font></b> <font color="#6b3e34">That You <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Love</b> <font color="#6b3e34">Me</font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

305
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="25"><font color="#3d8afc"><b><font color="#f76bb3">Whisper</font></b> <font color="#6b3e34">That You <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Love</b> <font color="#6b3e34">Me</font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

306
00:23:30,890 --> 00:23:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua's cold gaze, his cold voice...
I can't breathe.</font>

307
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, Prince Aqua, look at me.</font>

